title: BBC Football Focus 720p 50fps 09.09.2017
description:
Football Focus comes live from Brighton and Hove Albion as Dan Walker and guests Danny Murphy and Matthew Upson preview a stellar weekend of Premier League action. Seagulls' manager Chris Hughton talks exclusively to the show and there are interviews with Tottenham's Eric Dier, Manchester United striker Romelu Lukaku and Leicester winger Mark Albrighton. Mark Clemmit travels to Leeds to speak to manager Thomas Christiansen about their strong start to the Championship season.  

Video : AVC, 50 fps, 1280 x 720, 5053 Kbps  
Audio : AAC, 48 KHz, 96 kbps
